Column.Name: RECORDED_DATE
Display.Name: RECORDED_DATE
Description: Date the document was recorded by the Recorded of Deeds

Column.Name: EXECUTED_DATE
Display.Name: EXECUTED_DATE
Description: Date the Deed was signed by parties NOTE: Many dates have been entered with data entry errors in Source Files, see e.g. Doc # 0600445026 Transfer File 2006.csv

Column.Name: PIN
Display.Name: PIN
Description: Unique Permanent Identification Number for each property. All PINs are 14 digits: 2 digits for area + 2 digits for sub area + 2 digits for block + 2 digits for parcel + 4 digits for the multicode

Column.Name: TOWN_NAME
Display.Name: TOWN_NAME
Description: Township name as assigned by the Assessment office. An interactive map is available at https://maps.cookcountyil.gov/cookviewer/
